title: Maddie Clifton // 65
description:
In 1998, an 8-year-old girl living in Jacksonville, Florida went missing from her neighborhood after playing golf with a man up the street. After hundreds of volunteers banned together with local police, they made a horrifying discovery. This is the murder of Maddie Clifton.
